1. Baskı
Legal English with 14 Lectures and Practical Tips
https://imageserver.kitapyurdu.com/select.php?imageid=6293944&width=500&isWatermarked=true
2018-05-31
 25,33
This Book does not make you repeat a number of words without any context. Rather, this Book teaches you commonly used words, phrases, and structures in Legal English by giving a comprehensive understanding of 14 Subjects of Law which are Constitutional Law, Contract Law, International Law, International Investment Law, Turkish Commercial Law, International Intellectual Property Law, International Commercial Law, INCOTERMS, International Commercial Arbitration, EU Law, International Civil Procedure, Legal Writing and IRAC Rule, Writing Legal Memorandum. This Book consists of both an academic and practical component. The structure of each lecture is as follows: 1. Commonly used words and structures in Law Language 2. Terminology and Reading 3. Free writing Exercises 4. Legal Tips. Legal English is a big key for lawyers' success. This Book provides you everything you need in this process. The structure of this Book gives you the best way to learn and master necessary vocabulary. This method will take you one-step further in your legal career.
